Local Files
===========

You need to add:

1) Local configuration file php_code/local.php, described in "Config" section
2) Local gfx files in path that can be found by $pic_path set in config
2a) Flag svg-files in a "flags" subdirectory of some gfx directory
3) php_code/flagspecs.php, usually generated by private/build_flagspec.sh


Config
======

Local configuration is in file php_code/local.php.
Values to configure:

$metaURL
  Address that Freeciv servers should use to contact this metaserver. This is only
  used to instruct users. Default metaserver should probably set it NULL, others may
  want to set it to "http://$_SERVER[SERVER_NAME]$_SERVER[REQUEST_URI]"

$metaserver_url_path
  Metaserver directory relative to server root. Last "/" is required, except if this is
  pointing to webserver root.
  Default value is "" (webserver root)

$metaserver_root
  Filesystem path to metaserver root.
  Default value is "$_SERVER[DOCUMENT_ROOT]$metaserver_url_path"

$fcdb_default_db
  Name of the default database
  Default value is "default"

$fcdb_metaserver_db
  Name of the metaserver database
  Default value is "metaserver"

$fcdb_username
  MySQL username
  Default value is "dude"

$fcdb_pw
  MySQL password
  Default value is '' (no password)

$pic_paths
  Array of image search directories. Maps between filesystem layout and
  webserver layout.

  Default value searches from pics subdirectories under metaserver directory and webserver 
  root directory:
    $metaserver_root . "pics/" => $metaserver_url_path . "pics/",
    $_SERVER[DOCUMENT_ROOT]/pics/ => "pics/"

$webmaster_email
  Email address for webmaster
  Default value is NULL

$webmaster_addr
  Webmaster URL
  Default value
    if $webmaster_email set: "mailto:$webmaster_email"
    otherwise NULL

$webmaster_name
  Name of the webmaster.
  Default value is "Webmaster"

$bugs_addr
  Bug report URL
  Default value is NULL

$bugs_name
  Where to send bug reports
  Default value is NULL

$metaserver_header
  Main header to display on metaserver page
  Default value is "Freeciv servers around the world"
